# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
/target/

# Generated by Tauri
# will have schema files for capabilities auto-completion
/gen/schemas

# iOS project is still pure scaffolding — treat as build artifacts.
/gen/ios

# The Android project is hand-edited (custom Activities, services,
# accessibility config, signed build.gradle.kts) AND has to build on CI,
# so it is tracked rather than regenerated. The project's own nested
# .gitignore files (gen/android/.gitignore, gen/android/app/.gitignore)
# still exclude the machine/build/tauri-generated bits — build dirs,
# .gradle caches, local.properties, tauri.properties, the generated/
# Kotlin, and jniLibs .so. We only add protections for the release
# signing material, which those don't cover.
/gen/android/keystore/
/gen/android/keystore.properties
*.jks
